    "## Solutions to Limits and Derivatives Quiz",
    "",
    "### Multiple Choice Answers",
    "",
    "**1)** c) 4 (after factoring: $\\frac{(x-2)(x+2)}{x-2} = x+2$, at x=2: 4)",
