    "### Short Answer Solutions",
    "",
    "**11)** $\\lim_{x \\to 3} \\frac{x^2 - 9}{x - 3} = \\lim_{x \\to 3} \\frac{(x-3)(x+3)}{x-3} = \\lim_{x \\to 3} (x+3) = 6$",
    "",
    "**12)** No, it has a corner discontinuity at x = 0 (removable discontinuity)",
    "",
    "**13)** f'(x) = 2 cos(2x) (chain rule: d/dx sin(u) = cos(u) * du/dx, u = 2x, du/dx = 2)",
    "",
    "**14)** Let u = x^2 + 1, y = u^3, dy/dx = dy/du * du/dx = 3u^2 * 2x = 6x(x^2 + 1)^2",
    "",
    "**15)** $\\lim_{x \\to 0} \\frac{1 - \\cos x}{x^2} = \\frac{1}{2}$ (second remarkable limit)",
    "",
    "**16)** f'(1) = 2(1) = 2, tangent line: y - 1 = 2(x - 1), y = 2x - 1",
    "",
    "**17)** $\\lim_{x \\to 0} \\frac{e^x - 1}{x} = \\lim_{x \\to 0} \\frac{e^x}{1} = 1$",
    "",
    "**18)** y' = 2e^{2x}, y'' = 4e^{2x}",
    "",
    "**19)** dx/dt = -sin t, dy/dt = cos t, dy/dx = cos t / (-sin t) = -cot t, at t = π/4: -cot(π/4) = -1",
    "",
    "**20)** ln y = x ln x, d/dx ln y = ln x + x * (1/x) = ln x + 1, dy/dx = y(ln x + 1) = x^x (ln x + 1)"
  ],
